{
  "stem": "1860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But nevertheless, we-- we managed to convince them and-- with the help of this-- my father's business friend who we are that we are inmates of-- previous inmates of concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were fantastic, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They placed us in homes for repatriates and-- and fed us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where we waited for our papers to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right after the war, the only person we spoke to was my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- for-- for weeks, we kept telling him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he just listened to us with wide open eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Couldn't understand, couldn't grasp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, he made-- first he said, if you were not my wife and my daughter, I would never believe it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then he said, I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If my family's hungry, I would go out and get them bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it just-- it was impossible to-- to-- to describe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not-- not bad, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a nervous stomach, but otherwise I was all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so was my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- when we were in Rotterdam, I remember my brother was at that time-- he was with the British Royal Air Force, Polish division.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a bombardier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He volunteered during the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came to visit us in Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, it was an extremely emotional reunion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and then, after we got our papers, we went to United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- for a while, we were toying with the idea, maybe with bringing her over here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that point, she was already an old lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to me, she always appeared to be old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She was probably younger than I am today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we felt that she would be completely lost here without her friends and her-- and knowledge of language.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
